1
00:00:11,883 --> 00:00:13,685
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was so awesome!</font>

2
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:15,988
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Listen.</font>

3
00:00:17,856 --> 00:00:20,325
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How can you get so excited
about other people's relationships?</font>

4
00:00:20,993 --> 00:00:24,396
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! I was saving that for last!</font>

5
00:00:25,397 --> 00:00:27,799
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The croquettes you make
are absolutely delicious.</font>

6
00:00:31,470 --> 00:00:33,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you like most about them?</font>

7
00:00:33,839 --> 00:00:35,107
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Must be the potato.</font>

8
00:00:35,173 --> 00:00:36,808
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't hang out
with you mushy love birds.</font>

9
00:00:36,875 --> 00:00:37,843
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're not mushy...</font>

10
00:00:37,909 --> 00:00:39,645
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's more fun hanging with cute girls.
Later.</font>

11
00:00:43,081 --> 00:00:44,750
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mushy love birds!</font>

12
00:00:46,385 --> 00:00:49,054
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What would you do
if I said that I liked Nao?</font>

13
00:00:52,724 --> 00:00:53,959
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you?</font>

14
00:00:57,696 --> 00:01:00,966
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, seriously...</font>

15
00:01:07,205 --> 00:01:09,608
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just thinking about you liking her</font>

16
00:01:12,010 --> 00:01:13,745
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">troubles me.</font>

17
00:01:20,652 --> 00:01:21,887
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was joking!</font>

18
00:01:25,557 --> 00:01:27,192
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell?</font>

19
00:01:27,392 --> 00:01:28,894
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You could make a better joke than that!</font>

20
00:01:31,396 --> 00:01:32,497
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

21
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:36,101
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

22
00:01:36,868 --> 00:01:37,903
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

23
00:01:38,470 --> 00:01:39,571
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong?</font>

24
00:01:40,472 --> 00:01:41,506
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing.</font>

25
00:01:42,774 --> 00:01:46,378
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hasn't he been acting strange lately?</font>

26
00:01:49,114 --> 00:01:49,948
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

27
00:01:51,450 --> 00:01:53,485
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And he got into that fight before.</font>

28
00:02:00,759 --> 00:02:02,461
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not like you, Uehara.</font>

29
00:02:03,662 --> 00:02:06,465
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You never used to worry about
other people like this.</font>

30
00:02:09,735 --> 00:02:11,303
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I feel a bit lonely.</font>

31
00:02:12,337 --> 00:02:14,406
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All you care about now is Natsume!</font>

32
00:02:14,473 --> 00:02:15,674
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Idiot.</font>

33
00:02:18,443 --> 00:02:19,444
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">BASED ON THE COMIC SERIES</font>

34
00:02:19,511 --> 00:02:21,313
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>GOOD MORNING CALL
AND <i>GOOD MORNING KISS BY YUE TAKASUKA</i></i></font>

35
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:20,806
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">By the way, did you hear
about the team trip?</font>

36
00:03:21,873 --> 00:03:25,677
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're on a tight budget,
so the freshmen and I will stay behind.</font>

37
00:03:25,977 --> 00:03:29,414
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really? It'll be tough
without you, Nanase.</font>

38
00:03:30,315 --> 00:03:32,684
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We don't mind if you stay
in the same room with us, so come!</font>

39
00:03:32,784 --> 00:03:33,819
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right, Daichi?</font>

40
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:36,488
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She can't do that!
What are you talking about?</font>

41
00:03:36,588 --> 00:03:37,422
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right?</font>

42
00:03:38,290 --> 00:03:39,825
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I...</font>

43
00:03:39,891 --> 00:03:42,828
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can't. You're a girl, Nanase.</font>

44
00:03:43,728 --> 00:03:46,231
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll massage your feet
for you if you want.</font>

45
00:03:46,331 --> 00:03:48,066
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Never mind! No, thanks!</font>

46
00:03:48,133 --> 00:03:49,301
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll pass!</font>

47
00:03:57,709 --> 00:03:59,277
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-What?</font>

48
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:06,117
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to make cheering flags
for all of the players for the away game.</font>

49
00:04:07,452 --> 00:04:08,520
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is last year's design.</font>

50
00:04:09,221 --> 00:04:10,488
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">One of these for every player?</font>

51
00:04:10,555 --> 00:04:13,258
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But if you need them
by the day after tomorrow...</font>

52
00:04:13,358 --> 00:04:15,026
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll be away on a field trip.</font>

53
00:04:15,627 --> 00:04:16,461
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please!</font>

54
00:04:17,729 --> 00:04:19,030
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know it's a bit difficult.</font>

55
00:04:19,598 --> 00:04:21,833
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I can't join them,</font>

56
00:04:22,300 --> 00:04:24,035
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and I really want these made!</font>

57
00:04:27,706 --> 00:04:28,540
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll do it!</font>

58
00:04:29,007 --> 00:04:29,841
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa?</font>

59
00:04:30,909 --> 00:04:32,978
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase, I'll do my best.</font>

60
00:04:33,812 --> 00:04:36,681
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa, so you're
in the handicrafts club.</font>

61
00:04:36,781 --> 00:04:39,551
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry to say this,
but Yoshikawa on her own...</font>

62
00:04:40,752 --> 00:04:42,120
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll help her.</font>

63
00:04:45,724 --> 00:04:46,791
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please.</font>

64
00:04:52,731 --> 00:04:55,200
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>What would you do
if I said that I liked Nao?</i></font>

65
00:04:57,135 --> 00:04:58,603
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That troubles me.</font>

66
00:05:11,182 --> 00:05:12,617
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello.</font>

67
00:05:25,497 --> 00:05:26,665
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko.</font>

68
00:05:31,503 --> 00:05:34,239
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you serious? About Uehara?</font>

69
00:05:36,241 --> 00:05:37,075
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I am.</font>

70
00:05:39,811 --> 00:05:40,879
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You see,</font>

71
00:05:42,013 --> 00:05:46,017
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">this is the first time
I've actually grown feelings for someone.</font>

72
00:05:51,122 --> 00:05:53,725
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It might be my first love. At my age!</font>

73
00:05:56,428 --> 00:05:58,663
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I want to cherish it.</font>

74
00:06:00,966 --> 00:06:03,468
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even if it ends up hurting somebody?</font>

75
00:06:04,135 --> 00:06:06,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Even if it does.
-Saeko...</font>

76
00:06:06,438 --> 00:06:07,639
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's the way it is.</font>

77
00:06:08,606 --> 00:06:10,108
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you disagree, Natsume?</font>

78
00:06:15,013 --> 00:06:17,482
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You like Yoshikawa, don't you?</font>

79
00:06:21,686 --> 00:06:23,421
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Well...
-Can you endure it?</font>

80
00:06:24,089 --> 00:06:25,991
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The person you love
smiling at someone else.</font>

81
00:06:36,935 --> 00:06:39,571
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In that case,
that's the extent of your feelings.</font>

82
00:06:41,539 --> 00:06:42,674
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you know, Saeko...</font>

83
00:06:42,741 --> 00:06:44,776
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That means you don't like her.
-I do.</font>

84
00:06:51,983 --> 00:06:56,221
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thinking it and saying it
are different things.</font>

85
00:06:58,156 --> 00:07:00,625
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You and I...</font>

86
00:07:02,260 --> 00:07:03,928
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We've fallen in love for the first time.</font>

87
00:07:04,763 --> 00:07:07,665
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If we don't acknowledge it ourselves,
no one else will.</font>

88
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko.</font>

89
00:07:16,007 --> 00:07:16,908
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you just trick me?</font>

90
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:20,612
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess it's the wisdom of age.</font>

91
00:07:23,214 --> 00:07:24,049
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

92
00:07:24,549 --> 00:07:26,084
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Excuse us.</font>

93
00:07:26,584 --> 00:07:27,719
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello.</font>

94
00:07:29,788 --> 00:07:32,323
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank goodness. You are here, Natsume.</font>

95
00:07:32,757 --> 00:07:35,460
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara said you would probably be here.</font>

96
00:07:36,561 --> 00:07:37,395
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

97
00:07:39,964 --> 00:07:41,266
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you happen...</font>

98
00:07:43,334 --> 00:07:44,569
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to overhear our conversation?</font>

99
00:07:50,341 --> 00:07:51,443
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

100
00:07:51,776 --> 00:07:53,011
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello.</font>

101
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,980
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're Uehara's girlfriend, right?</font>

102
00:07:59,217 --> 00:08:01,453
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. Nao Yoshikawa.</font>

103
00:08:02,454 --> 00:08:03,555
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was so busy before.</font>

104
00:08:03,655 --> 00:08:05,790
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry I never
introduced myself properly.</font>

105
00:08:07,592 --> 00:08:10,028
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I am always in Uehara's debt.</font>

106
00:08:12,530 --> 00:08:13,698
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's all right.
-Nao.</font>

107
00:08:14,799 --> 00:08:17,502
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's up? What brings you here?</font>

108
00:08:18,403 --> 00:08:19,304
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, right.</font>

109
00:08:19,370 --> 00:08:22,040
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have a favor to ask you, Natsume.</font>

110
00:08:24,809 --> 00:08:26,478
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Please!
-Please!</font>

111
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,714
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop bowing.</font>

112
00:08:30,348 --> 00:08:32,851
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please. I have to get them completed.</font>

113
00:08:33,751 --> 00:08:37,522
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Our club chief said we could take
on the job if you help, Natsume.</font>

114
00:08:38,389 --> 00:08:39,457
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please!</font>

115
00:08:41,392 --> 00:08:42,260
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

116
00:08:43,194 --> 00:08:44,496
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please!</font>

117
00:08:47,966 --> 00:08:48,933
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess I have no choice.</font>

118
00:08:49,667 --> 00:08:51,269
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Natsume!</font>

119
00:08:51,369 --> 00:08:52,604
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You saved me.</font>

120
00:08:53,571 --> 00:08:55,273
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now that's settled, let's get to it!</font>

121
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:07,886
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry for dragging you all into this.</font>

122
00:09:10,622 --> 00:09:11,890
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's totally fine.</font>

123
00:09:14,893 --> 00:09:15,994
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Actually, Nanase.</font>

124
00:09:16,594 --> 00:09:19,898
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Before, you said there was someone
you liked on the handball team.</font>

125
00:09:20,231 --> 00:09:21,799
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's why you're so keen to make these.</font>

126
00:09:24,235 --> 00:09:26,971
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just can't make up my mind.</font>

127
00:09:30,408 --> 00:09:32,877
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I decided not to tell him how I feel.</font>

128
00:09:34,512 --> 00:09:38,249
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If it's going to trouble him,
it's best we just stay friends.</font>

129
00:09:41,019 --> 00:09:42,520
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And if we're always together,</font>

130
00:09:43,054 --> 00:09:45,456
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I figure someday he may
end up falling for me.</font>

131
00:09:46,591 --> 00:09:48,293
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That goes without saying.</font>

132
00:09:50,562 --> 00:09:54,566
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When Uehara and I first met,
it was the worst.</font>

133
00:09:54,999 --> 00:09:57,402
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And there was someone
who had feelings for him.</font>

134
00:09:59,637 --> 00:10:03,341
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But we were always together, and then...</font>

135
00:10:03,408 --> 00:10:05,543
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not going to be that easy.</font>

136
00:10:06,844 --> 00:10:10,648
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're not living together
like you and Uehara were.</font>

137
00:10:14,752 --> 00:10:16,187
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, I've decided</font>

138
00:10:16,588 --> 00:10:21,192
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to quit acting like a heroine in a tragedy
who suffers because we're only friends.</font>

139
00:10:21,526 --> 00:10:22,994
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And to be by his side,</font>

140
00:10:23,194 --> 00:10:24,329
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">as friends.</font>

141
00:10:25,964 --> 00:10:28,900
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's much better than
not being able to see him anymore.</font>

142
00:10:32,103 --> 00:10:33,304
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase.</font>

143
00:10:34,973 --> 00:10:37,942
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is my decision.</font>

144
00:10:38,776 --> 00:10:40,612
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll give this to him
as proof of my friendship.</font>

145
00:10:42,914 --> 00:10:45,049
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe it's just for myself,</font>

146
00:10:46,618 --> 00:10:48,286
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I really want him to have it.</font>

147
00:11:01,366 --> 00:11:02,934
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's do our best!</font>

148
00:11:04,869 --> 00:11:05,903
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

149
00:11:07,605 --> 00:11:10,208
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not much of a reward,
but I'll go buy us some drinks.</font>

150
00:11:10,675 --> 00:11:12,176
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll come with you.</font>

151
00:11:12,277 --> 00:11:13,811
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll go.</font>

152
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,848
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't mind.</font>

153
00:11:23,588 --> 00:11:25,189
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What you said before, do you mean it?</font>

154
00:11:26,824 --> 00:11:27,659
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

155
00:11:28,860 --> 00:11:30,762
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About staying friends with him.</font>

156
00:11:32,764 --> 00:11:34,465
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you mean?</font>

157
00:11:37,201 --> 00:11:39,203
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Real feelings are meaningless.</font>

158
00:11:41,873 --> 00:11:45,443
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The point is how you want to see things.</font>

159
00:12:02,694 --> 00:12:03,695
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

160
00:12:04,095 --> 00:12:05,263
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bathroom?</font>

161
00:12:05,863 --> 00:12:06,864
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

162
00:12:07,765 --> 00:12:09,334
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Today, Yoshikawa was...</font>

163
00:12:11,402 --> 00:12:12,537
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about Yoshikawa?</font>

164
00:12:13,438 --> 00:12:14,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's nothing.</font>

165
00:12:17,408 --> 00:12:19,877
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If it's nothing,
why are you fidgeting like that?</font>

166
00:12:28,252 --> 00:12:31,622
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She said she was going to
make croquettes tonight.</font>

167
00:12:33,891 --> 00:12:35,093
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's why you're so giddy.</font>

168
00:12:35,793 --> 00:12:37,395
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I am not giddy.</font>

169
00:12:37,895 --> 00:12:40,531
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's just a really good cook.</font>

170
00:12:45,269 --> 00:12:46,771
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How unfortunate.</font>

171
00:12:47,972 --> 00:12:52,076
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was going to treat you to dinner tonight
for making you work late on your birthday.</font>

172
00:12:54,112 --> 00:12:55,279
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Should we move it to tomorrow?</font>

173
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,215
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

174
00:12:57,415 --> 00:12:59,083
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I believe in clearing out my debts.</font>

175
00:13:00,618 --> 00:13:01,652
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you very much.</font>

176
00:13:02,587 --> 00:13:03,554
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Tomorrow it is.</font>

177
00:13:03,654 --> 00:13:05,423
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Think about what you would like to eat.</font>

178
00:13:05,490 --> 00:13:06,357
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

179
00:13:11,863 --> 00:13:12,730
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>What are you doing?</i></font>

180
00:13:14,365 --> 00:13:16,234
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Making cheering flags
for the handball team.</font>

181
00:13:16,401 --> 00:13:18,903
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They have to be done
by the day after tomorrow.</font>

182
00:13:24,242 --> 00:13:28,579
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Also, tomorrow night we may end up
having to work here.</font>

183
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:31,015
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Club time alone isn't enough to do it all.</font>

184
00:13:31,082 --> 00:13:33,251
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't need to make dinner
tomorrow night.</font>

185
00:13:35,586 --> 00:13:37,388
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay. Sorry.</font>

186
00:13:37,955 --> 00:13:40,658
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See, tomorrow...</font>

187
00:13:43,060 --> 00:13:44,128
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong?</font>

188
00:13:49,567 --> 00:13:50,868
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who's coming?</font>

189
00:13:53,604 --> 00:13:57,408
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase from the handball team, Ota,
and Natsume, maybe.</font>

190
00:13:57,508 --> 00:14:00,178
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right. So that's why you were looking
for Natsume today.</font>

191
00:14:00,278 --> 00:14:01,679
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

192
00:14:02,413 --> 00:14:05,550
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume is so good at needlework!</font>

193
00:14:06,751 --> 00:14:08,486
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really?
-Yes.</font>

194
00:14:11,389 --> 00:14:12,323
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So,</font>

195
00:14:13,825 --> 00:14:14,992
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">sorry.</font>

196
00:14:17,728 --> 00:14:19,630
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm breaking my promise.</font>

197
00:14:26,137 --> 00:14:28,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Remember what you said, Uehara?</font>

198
00:14:30,842 --> 00:14:34,178
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Don't bring any other men to your place."</font>

199
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:37,348
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The man is Natsume.</font>

200
00:14:39,851 --> 00:14:40,852
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That is true.</font>

201
00:14:46,791 --> 00:14:47,859
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you smiling about?</font>

202
00:14:52,396 --> 00:14:53,965
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you psychic?</font>

203
00:14:54,031 --> 00:14:56,267
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know all your habits by now.</font>

204
00:15:00,605 --> 00:15:01,706
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's love.</font>

205
00:15:01,772 --> 00:15:04,375
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's natural when we've lived together
for a year.</font>

206
00:15:07,445 --> 00:15:09,347
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>It's not going to be that easy.</i></font>

207
00:15:10,081 --> 00:15:14,685
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're not living together
like you and Uehara were.</font>

208
00:15:33,170 --> 00:15:34,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

209
00:15:37,842 --> 00:15:39,343
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If we</font>

210
00:15:41,646 --> 00:15:44,315
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">hadn't lived together...</font>

211
00:15:52,723 --> 00:15:54,592
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's nothing.</font>

212
00:16:04,335 --> 00:16:05,469
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume.</font>

213
00:16:13,844 --> 00:16:15,179
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Natsume.</font>

214
00:16:16,614 --> 00:16:17,915
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you walking away?</font>

215
00:16:21,152 --> 00:16:22,787
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is it? Do you need me for something?</font>

216
00:16:23,287 --> 00:16:24,121
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

217
00:16:25,156 --> 00:16:27,391
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You didn't show up
for molecular biology today.</font>

218
00:16:28,159 --> 00:16:30,761
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I have lots of stuff going on,
like a date and another date.</font>

219
00:16:30,828 --> 00:16:32,063
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

220
00:16:33,331 --> 00:16:34,565
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, what's up?</font>

221
00:16:34,899 --> 00:16:38,102
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hear the club is up against the wall.</font>

222
00:16:38,869 --> 00:16:39,971
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Kind of.</font>

223
00:16:40,204 --> 00:16:42,940
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry she dragged you
into things again.</font>

224
00:16:44,375 --> 00:16:45,910
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm used to it now.</font>

225
00:16:46,277 --> 00:16:48,145
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Plus I'm the star of the handicrafts club.</font>

226
00:16:48,613 --> 00:16:49,647
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I hear.</font>

227
00:16:51,515 --> 00:16:54,251
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Apparently we're working at Nao's later,
so I'll be heading over.</font>

228
00:16:54,352 --> 00:16:55,686
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. I heard.</font>

229
00:16:56,153 --> 00:16:57,021
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't be there.</font>

230
00:16:58,356 --> 00:17:00,057
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-I'm having dinner with Saeko.</font>

231
00:17:00,992 --> 00:17:02,326
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What the hell?
-What?</font>

232
00:17:02,393 --> 00:17:04,929
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You and Saeko, just the two of you?
Is that okay?</font>

233
00:17:05,229 --> 00:17:06,998
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What do you mean?
-Having dinner together...</font>

234
00:17:07,098 --> 00:17:08,933
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If it's dinner you want, let me treat you.</font>

235
00:17:14,872 --> 00:17:15,973
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's up?</font>

236
00:17:18,509 --> 00:17:19,777
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've been acting weird lately.</font>

237
00:17:24,415 --> 00:17:25,449
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell me</font>

238
00:17:29,787 --> 00:17:30,955
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you have feelings for Saeko...</font>

239
00:17:31,022 --> 00:17:32,189
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not it.</font>

240
00:17:35,426 --> 00:17:37,061
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well,</font>

241
00:17:37,928 --> 00:17:40,831
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you had a thing for older women.</font>

242
00:17:40,898 --> 00:17:42,767
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You're mentally old.
-You...</font>

243
00:17:42,833 --> 00:17:45,236
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The way you take a step back
and look at the big picture.</font>

244
00:17:45,302 --> 00:17:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The way you're like, "I know everything."</font>

245
00:17:48,639 --> 00:17:51,876
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a pain in the neck sometimes.</font>

246
00:17:54,945 --> 00:17:56,447
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not a compliment, is it?</font>

247
00:17:56,781 --> 00:18:01,152
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it's always for the benefit of others.</font>

248
00:18:03,354 --> 00:18:07,158
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't do that for others,
so I really respect that.</font>

249
00:18:08,292 --> 00:18:09,460
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Something like that.</font>

250
00:18:13,264 --> 00:18:14,665
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like what?</font>

251
00:18:15,599 --> 00:18:20,137
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, when you said that you liked her,</font>

252
00:18:21,706 --> 00:18:24,308
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess I was really stunned.</font>

253
00:18:27,511 --> 00:18:30,081
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It felt threatening, I guess.</font>

254
00:18:32,650 --> 00:18:33,851
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

255
00:18:35,019 --> 00:18:37,688
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What was I talking about?</font>

256
00:18:39,690 --> 00:18:40,825
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know.</font>

257
00:18:40,925 --> 00:18:44,762
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Right. About you liking Saeko.
-I told you...</font>

258
00:18:44,829 --> 00:18:48,165
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry. I have to get to the lab.</font>

259
00:18:48,265 --> 00:18:49,100
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you.</font>

260
00:18:53,537 --> 00:18:55,272
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I had no idea!</font>

261
00:18:55,372 --> 00:18:58,642
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you're in love with me, Natsume?</font>

262
00:19:04,014 --> 00:19:05,216
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you looking so stylish?</font>

263
00:19:05,683 --> 00:19:07,918
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I always dress like this.</font>

264
00:19:13,591 --> 00:19:14,725
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko.</font>

265
00:19:17,862 --> 00:19:19,296
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's just no way.</font>

266
00:19:19,463 --> 00:19:20,331
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

267
00:19:21,899 --> 00:19:23,434
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want to betray him.</font>

268
00:19:27,438 --> 00:19:29,874
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He seems to think I'm some amazing guy.</font>

269
00:19:32,443 --> 00:19:33,544
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And you're okay with that?</font>

270
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:38,849
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm an old man inside.</font>

271
00:19:39,817 --> 00:19:41,285
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are those your real feelings?</font>

272
00:19:44,488 --> 00:19:46,423
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Real feelings are meaningless.</font>

273
00:19:48,359 --> 00:19:50,461
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The point is how you want to see things.</font>

274
00:19:55,533 --> 00:19:59,904
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Have a nice day.</font>

275
00:20:04,975 --> 00:20:05,943
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello.</font>

276
00:20:06,043 --> 00:20:07,111
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello.</font>

277
00:20:26,797 --> 00:20:27,832
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

278
00:20:28,666 --> 00:20:31,001
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume. Come in.</font>

279
00:20:31,101 --> 00:20:32,970
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thank you.
-Of course.</font>

280
00:20:41,645 --> 00:20:42,847
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume?</font>

281
00:20:50,688 --> 00:20:53,357
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here it is! Done!</font>

282
00:20:56,727 --> 00:20:58,729
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">YOSHITO KOBAYASHI
HANDBALL CLUB</font>

283
00:20:58,829 --> 00:20:59,797
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How nice.</font>

284
00:21:02,333 --> 00:21:04,602
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It took a whole day though.</font>

285
00:21:05,069 --> 00:21:06,036
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

286
00:21:07,204 --> 00:21:08,339
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

287
00:21:08,606 --> 00:21:10,307
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Next...</font>

288
00:21:11,075 --> 00:21:12,476
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">DAICHI SHINOZAKI
HANDBALL CLUB</font>

289
00:21:13,444 --> 00:21:14,578
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi's.</font>

290
00:21:21,552 --> 00:21:22,620
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just...</font>

291
00:21:23,287 --> 00:21:24,355
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

292
00:21:24,455 --> 00:21:26,757
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why don't you let Nanase do Daichi's?</font>

293
00:21:27,024 --> 00:21:28,959
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's the star of the handball team.</font>

294
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:30,461
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Right?
-Right?</font>

295
00:21:31,028 --> 00:21:32,796
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

296
00:21:32,863 --> 00:21:37,601
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi is the only one
who would accept this.</font>

297
00:21:37,668 --> 00:21:39,637
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you realize how bad it is?</font>

298
00:21:39,737 --> 00:21:42,473
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi would be a bit understanding
even if it's bad.</font>

299
00:21:43,007 --> 00:21:43,941
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

300
00:21:44,408 --> 00:21:46,543
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, Nanase,</font>

301
00:21:46,877 --> 00:21:50,781
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll do that one, so please do this one.</font>

302
00:22:01,358 --> 00:22:02,426
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

303
00:22:17,875 --> 00:22:19,276
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase?</font>

304
00:22:29,019 --> 00:22:30,154
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Your girlfriend,</i></font>

305
00:22:31,055 --> 00:22:32,890
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">did you fall in love with her right away?</font>

306
00:22:37,728 --> 00:22:39,229
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was relatively quick.</font>

307
00:22:41,565 --> 00:22:44,101
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come? What was it about her?</font>

308
00:22:45,436 --> 00:22:46,904
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do I have to answer that?</font>

309
00:22:46,971 --> 00:22:49,740
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Is it something you can't say?</font>

310
00:22:49,807 --> 00:22:51,375
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's nothing like that.</font>

311
00:22:51,475 --> 00:22:52,910
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then you can tell me.</font>

312
00:22:57,448 --> 00:23:00,050
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, this looks good.</font>

313
00:23:12,930 --> 00:23:14,365
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For various reasons,</font>

314
00:23:16,367 --> 00:23:19,036
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">we lived together before we dated.</font>

315
00:23:20,637 --> 00:23:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Together?</font>

316
00:23:22,072 --> 00:23:23,340
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a long story, but...</font>

317
00:23:23,407 --> 00:23:24,608
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hang on.</font>

318
00:23:25,943 --> 00:23:26,910
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Excuse me!
-Yes?</font>

319
00:23:27,011 --> 00:23:28,679
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-One beer, please.
-Yes, ma'am.</font>

320
00:23:29,146 --> 00:23:31,915
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't listen to people talk about
their love life unless I'm drinking.</font>

321
00:23:35,019 --> 00:23:38,022
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">DAICHI SHINOZAKI
HANDBALL CLUB</font>

322
00:23:39,790 --> 00:23:40,824
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sorry!</font>

323
00:23:44,728 --> 00:23:47,498
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If we redo it from the lettering
we won't make it in time...</font>

324
00:23:47,598 --> 00:23:48,766
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ota, have some tea.</font>

325
00:23:48,866 --> 00:23:50,401
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I am truly sorry.</font>

326
00:23:55,439 --> 00:23:58,509
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll apologize to Daichi.</font>

327
00:23:58,609 --> 00:23:59,943
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Wait a second!
-I'll go apologize!</font>

328
00:24:00,778 --> 00:24:03,914
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is a surprise.
It'll be pointless if you spill the beans.</font>

329
00:24:05,616 --> 00:24:06,817
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

330
00:24:09,053 --> 00:24:11,188
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But...
-It's Daichi.</font>

331
00:24:14,992 --> 00:24:15,926
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

332
00:24:16,226 --> 00:24:19,229
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're taking the time to help me,
but I was so absent-minded.</font>

333
00:24:19,730 --> 00:24:21,598
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it was all my fault...</font>

334
00:24:22,066 --> 00:24:24,735
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The person I like is Daichi.</font>

335
00:24:26,937 --> 00:24:27,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

336
00:24:39,383 --> 00:24:40,784
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao really had no idea.</font>

337
00:24:40,884 --> 00:24:43,754
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even I figured it out.</font>

338
00:24:44,421 --> 00:24:45,422
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

339
00:24:46,857 --> 00:24:51,161
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But Daichi likes you, Yoshikawa, right?</font>

340
00:24:54,364 --> 00:24:57,267
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, that was a long time ago.</font>

341
00:24:57,367 --> 00:24:59,169
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's still true.</font>

342
00:24:59,803 --> 00:25:02,840
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If it weren't, how could he ignore
such a nice woman</font>

343
00:25:02,940 --> 00:25:04,341
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">who's right by his side?</font>

344
00:25:04,408 --> 00:25:05,576
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean yourself?</font>

345
00:25:06,176 --> 00:25:07,111
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

346
00:25:10,147 --> 00:25:11,181
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But.</font>

347
00:25:11,615 --> 00:25:12,783
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I made a decision.</font>

348
00:25:14,785 --> 00:25:19,089
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll put all of my thoughts about Daichi
into this, and seal them away.</font>

349
00:25:21,225 --> 00:25:22,860
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I can be with him as a friend.</font>

350
00:25:27,598 --> 00:25:31,068
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's okay.
We can just start over from scratch.</font>

351
00:25:31,902 --> 00:25:33,003
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's still time.</font>

352
00:25:39,143 --> 00:25:40,911
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe I should make something too.</font>

353
00:25:42,613 --> 00:25:44,281
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For a declaration of friendship.</font>

354
00:25:47,885 --> 00:25:49,553
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have feelings for someone, too.</font>

355
00:25:55,425 --> 00:25:59,596
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But why would you make
a declaration of friendship?</font>

356
00:25:59,696 --> 00:26:01,098
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Before that, the first thing</font>

357
00:26:01,165 --> 00:26:04,568
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-you should do...
-Because she's in love with someone else.</font>

358
00:26:14,011 --> 00:26:15,512
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is it...</font>

359
00:26:17,181 --> 00:26:18,549
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Could it be...</font>

360
00:26:19,283 --> 00:26:21,084
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's not Nanase.</font>

361
00:26:21,518 --> 00:26:24,121
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Obviously.
-You've got it totally wrong.</font>

362
00:26:25,122 --> 00:26:29,026
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But a declaration of friendship...</font>

363
00:26:29,126 --> 00:26:31,261
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's fine. Really.</font>

364
00:26:34,831 --> 00:26:36,700
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just wanted to tell you</font>

365
00:26:38,535 --> 00:26:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">because of how you cried, arguing that
having someone you want to be with</font>

366
00:26:42,105 --> 00:26:44,041
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">is what makes you happy.</font>

367
00:26:50,013 --> 00:26:52,115
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wasn't crying.</font>

368
00:26:52,216 --> 00:26:53,417
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You were crying.</font>

369
00:26:54,218 --> 00:26:55,319
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wasn't.</font>

370
00:26:56,019 --> 00:26:58,088
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe it looked that way to you, Natsume,</font>

371
00:26:58,188 --> 00:26:59,489
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I wasn't crying.</font>

372
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:02,459
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay! Let's get back to work.</font>

373
00:27:03,060 --> 00:27:05,028
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no time for chatting.</font>

374
00:27:05,229 --> 00:27:07,164
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the one who started it, Nanase.</font>

375
00:27:07,264 --> 00:27:08,298
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shut up.</font>

376
00:27:08,398 --> 00:27:10,300
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, let's keep working.</font>

377
00:27:12,569 --> 00:27:15,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This feels so nice.</font>

378
00:27:16,273 --> 00:27:17,241
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko.</font>

379
00:27:18,375 --> 00:27:19,910
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll get you a taxi.</font>

380
00:27:22,045 --> 00:27:23,347
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

381
00:27:37,928 --> 00:27:40,130
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe Ota forgot something here.</font>

382
00:27:41,932 --> 00:27:43,166
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

383
00:27:46,603 --> 00:27:48,739
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello!</font>

384
00:27:50,807 --> 00:27:51,642
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko?</font>

385
00:27:51,708 --> 00:27:53,043
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa. Sorry.</font>

386
00:27:53,143 --> 00:27:55,112
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko got a bit drunk.</font>

387
00:27:55,212 --> 00:27:57,614
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She wanted to pay a visit.
I said no, but she wouldn't listen.</font>

388
00:27:57,714 --> 00:27:59,683
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't take her back
to my place either.</font>

389
00:28:02,653 --> 00:28:03,520
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko?</font>

390
00:28:03,587 --> 00:28:05,555
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume! Give me a hand.</font>

391
00:28:06,189 --> 00:28:07,891
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko, get ahold of yourself.</font>

392
00:28:07,991 --> 00:28:10,594
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Natsume, you're here.</font>

393
00:28:10,694 --> 00:28:12,329
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

394
00:28:12,429 --> 00:28:13,330
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bathroom.</font>

395
00:28:13,397 --> 00:28:15,165
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Bathroom.</font>

396
00:28:15,265 --> 00:28:17,934
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa, sorry but Saeko seems
to be feeling unwell.</font>

397
00:28:18,568 --> 00:28:20,570
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure. Come in.</font>

398
00:28:30,914 --> 00:28:32,416
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry for intruding.</font>

399
00:28:36,219 --> 00:28:38,055
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why were you with Saeko?</font>

400
00:28:39,589 --> 00:28:40,724
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She asked me to dinner.</font>

401
00:28:40,824 --> 00:28:42,092
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The two of you?</font>

402
00:28:42,959 --> 00:28:43,960
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

403
00:28:45,762 --> 00:28:51,101
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you'd go along for a meal alone
with anyone who invites you.</font>

404
00:28:54,204 --> 00:28:56,506
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Or was it because it's Saeko?</font>

405
00:28:59,042 --> 00:29:01,044
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's no different from going
for a meal with Natsume.</font>

406
00:29:02,879 --> 00:29:04,614
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it's not the same.</font>

407
00:29:06,183 --> 00:29:08,218
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right. It's not the same.</font>

408
00:29:11,421 --> 00:29:13,790
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, when a man and a woman...</font>

409
00:29:13,890 --> 00:29:14,891
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop right there!</font>

410
00:29:15,625 --> 00:29:18,195
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We don't have time to chat.
We need to make these.</font>

411
00:29:18,829 --> 00:29:20,130
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look. Nanase will get angry.</font>

412
00:29:22,332 --> 00:29:23,600
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

413
00:29:24,701 --> 00:29:26,636
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Making cheering flags
for the handball team.</font>

414
00:29:28,805 --> 00:29:31,875
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to get these finished
by tomorrow no matter what.</font>

415
00:29:33,443 --> 00:29:35,345
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can you help with embroidery too, Saeko?</font>

416
00:29:36,847 --> 00:29:37,981
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Needlework?</font>

417
00:29:39,549 --> 00:29:40,650
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not a chance.</font>

418
00:29:40,817 --> 00:29:41,885
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course not.</font>

419
00:29:41,985 --> 00:29:43,120
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're insulting me.</font>

420
00:29:43,220 --> 00:29:44,154
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're imagining it.</font>

421
00:29:44,254 --> 00:29:47,023
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're going to be in the way,
please leave.</font>

422
00:29:48,024 --> 00:29:50,961
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so desperate!</font>

423
00:29:51,194 --> 00:29:52,429
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How cute!</font>

424
00:29:52,529 --> 00:29:54,297
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko, you're really drunk.</font>

425
00:29:54,398 --> 00:29:55,532
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's get you home.</font>

426
00:29:55,766 --> 00:29:56,767
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're going home.</font>

427
00:29:58,135 --> 00:30:00,003
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong with being desperate?</font>

428
00:30:01,471 --> 00:30:03,507
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to be with him even as friends,</font>

429
00:30:04,775 --> 00:30:07,144
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and I'm desperately working at that.
What's wrong with that?</font>

430
00:30:08,445 --> 00:30:11,148
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase. Saeko doesn't know
about your situation.</font>

431
00:30:13,283 --> 00:30:16,253
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So this is a love story?</font>

432
00:30:22,959 --> 00:30:27,063
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't really know your story,
but do you mean that?</font>

433
00:30:29,266 --> 00:30:30,400
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you mean?</font>

434
00:30:30,467 --> 00:30:32,669
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not striving to become lovers,</font>

435
00:30:32,769 --> 00:30:35,806
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and working desperately to stay
by his side as friends.</font>

436
00:30:35,906 --> 00:30:37,140
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't that weird?</font>

437
00:30:39,543 --> 00:30:42,412
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really want to be lovers,
but you're going to stay friends.</font>

438
00:30:43,146 --> 00:30:48,084
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You just think that's the better option
if things don't work out, right?</font>

439
00:30:48,785 --> 00:30:53,256
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aren't you just hurting yourself
by thinking that way?</font>

440
00:30:56,793 --> 00:30:58,061
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

441
00:30:59,329 --> 00:31:02,432
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you feel that way and you're by
his side, it's dishonest to him...</font>

442
00:31:02,499 --> 00:31:03,934
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko!</font>

443
00:31:06,203 --> 00:31:07,070
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

444
00:31:15,245 --> 00:31:17,781
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll go get you some water.</font>

445
00:31:19,216 --> 00:31:20,383
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

446
00:31:20,851 --> 00:31:24,855
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We better get back to work.
We don't have much time left.</font>

447
00:31:25,522 --> 00:31:26,857
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Better hurry.</font>

448
00:31:40,103 --> 00:31:41,104
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

449
00:31:44,341 --> 00:31:47,043
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't need to apologize, Uehara.</font>

450
00:31:47,143 --> 00:31:49,246
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I never told you
I was going out for dinner with Saeko.</font>

451
00:31:50,313 --> 00:31:51,248
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

452
00:31:53,183 --> 00:31:55,619
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">just thought it would be the same
as having dinner with Natsume.</font>

453
00:31:58,421 --> 00:31:59,289
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

454
00:32:04,494 --> 00:32:05,629
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

455
00:32:07,063 --> 00:32:09,499
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll help with the embroidery too.</font>

456
00:32:11,368 --> 00:32:13,870
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure. Thanks.</font>

457
00:32:20,076 --> 00:32:22,345
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko. Drink some water.</font>

458
00:32:22,445 --> 00:32:25,615
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you. You're so thoughtful.</font>

459
00:32:36,593 --> 00:32:37,727
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you okay?</font>

460
00:32:38,194 --> 00:32:40,397
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. I'm fine.</font>

461
00:32:41,197 --> 00:32:42,866
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're terrible at that.</font>

462
00:32:43,567 --> 00:32:45,669
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How clumsy can you get?</font>

463
00:32:46,703 --> 00:32:48,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, this is normal.</font>

464
00:32:50,607 --> 00:32:53,843
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That name card you made
for the softball game was terrible too.</font>

465
00:32:55,245 --> 00:32:57,414
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You only remember the bad stuff.</font>

466
00:32:57,514 --> 00:32:58,715
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How could I forget it?</font>

467
00:32:58,815 --> 00:33:00,450
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I need a break.</font>

468
00:33:01,351 --> 00:33:02,485
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you leaving?</font>

469
00:33:02,586 --> 00:33:04,588
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't treat me like I'm such a nuisance!</font>

470
00:33:04,654 --> 00:33:06,890
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I only said it
so you can maintain your dignity.</font>

471
00:33:06,957 --> 00:33:10,427
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're nosier than I expected, Natsume.</font>

472
00:33:11,027 --> 00:33:14,331
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you were a nicer guy,
right, Yoshikawa?</font>

473
00:33:16,633 --> 00:33:19,903
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, Natsume is quite popular though.</font>

474
00:33:20,704 --> 00:33:25,842
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I had to choose,
I would say Uehara is more my type.</font>

475
00:33:32,682 --> 00:33:33,950
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

476
00:33:34,150 --> 00:33:35,986
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, see.</font>

477
00:33:36,086 --> 00:33:39,022
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think Yoshikawa has a good eye for men.</font>

478
00:33:41,992 --> 00:33:43,660
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

479
00:33:43,727 --> 00:33:45,462
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm envious.</font>

480
00:33:45,695 --> 00:33:49,466
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You met by chance
and snagged such a nice guy.</font>

481
00:33:50,567 --> 00:33:52,102
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-I heard all about it.</font>

482
00:33:52,202 --> 00:33:53,603
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How you two met.</font>

483
00:33:56,006 --> 00:33:57,374
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She kept asking me about it.</font>

484
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:59,509
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I always wanted
to meet someone like that too.</font>

485
00:34:01,111 --> 00:34:04,814
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">To be frank,
I always thought it was strange</font>

486
00:34:05,215 --> 00:34:07,417
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that you were Uehara's girlfriend.</font>

487
00:34:08,351 --> 00:34:12,322
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But when I heard how you fell in love,
I totally got it.</font>

488
00:34:13,590 --> 00:34:18,194
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You just happened to be near him.
Why couldn't it have been me?</font>

489
00:34:30,006 --> 00:34:31,341
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hold on!</font>

490
00:34:31,975 --> 00:34:34,144
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't throw up.
Let's get you to the bathroom.</font>

491
00:34:35,211 --> 00:34:36,279
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez.</font>

492
00:34:47,757 --> 00:34:49,693
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll go buy some things.</font>

493
00:34:50,660 --> 00:34:51,494
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

494
00:34:59,135 --> 00:35:00,103
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

495
00:35:05,041 --> 00:35:05,975
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

496
00:35:08,445 --> 00:35:09,612
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you okay?</font>

497
00:35:16,720 --> 00:35:18,521
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, I'm fine.</font>

498
00:35:20,523 --> 00:35:22,192
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't look fine at all.</font>

499
00:35:28,364 --> 00:35:29,466
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

500
00:35:32,302 --> 00:35:33,536
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hate her.</font>

501
00:35:36,906 --> 00:35:37,907
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko.</font>

502
00:35:42,912 --> 00:35:43,780
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

503
00:35:46,249 --> 00:35:47,450
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hate her.</font>

504
00:35:53,623 --> 00:35:54,724
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

505
00:36:03,733 --> 00:36:04,801
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It can't be.</font>

506
00:36:11,508 --> 00:36:12,575
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

507
00:36:15,211 --> 00:36:17,213
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saeko is not a bad person.</font>

508
00:36:19,482 --> 00:36:23,019
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Me... I'm the one</font>

509
00:36:23,853 --> 00:36:26,856
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">who's to blame
because I don't have confidence in myself.</font>

510
00:36:32,262 --> 00:36:33,630
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It always worried me.</font>

511
00:36:38,468 --> 00:36:40,970
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That maybe Uehara and I
just dated by chance.</font>

512
00:36:42,172 --> 00:36:47,343
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And that things would have been different
if I didn't happen to be near him.</font>

513
00:36:49,746 --> 00:36:51,514
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've always thought about that.</font>

514
00:36:58,655 --> 00:37:02,125
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it is what it is.
Things ended up this way.</font>

515
00:37:07,864 --> 00:37:09,799
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know better than anybody</font>

516
00:37:12,468 --> 00:37:13,970
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that Uehara and I</font>

517
00:37:15,171 --> 00:37:17,273
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">are not the perfect match.</font>

518
00:37:23,713 --> 00:37:25,415
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know that, but...</font>

519
00:37:39,562 --> 00:37:41,064
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why did you do that?</font>

520
00:37:45,101 --> 00:37:46,002
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Force of habit.</font>

521
00:37:49,873 --> 00:37:51,975
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Whenever I kiss a crying girl
to console her,</font>

522
00:37:52,041 --> 00:37:53,877
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">she always stops crying.</font>

523
00:37:54,310 --> 00:37:55,378
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See? You stopped crying.</font>

524
00:38:06,656 --> 00:38:08,024
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really sorry!</font>

525
00:38:09,425 --> 00:38:12,095
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I'll head back.</font>

526
00:38:29,879 --> 00:38:30,880
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa.</font>

527
00:38:33,883 --> 00:38:34,817
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

528
00:38:34,884 --> 00:38:36,586
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where did you run off to?</font>

529
00:38:42,091 --> 00:38:44,761
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You shouldn't just leave like that.</font>

530
00:38:47,297 --> 00:38:48,331
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

531
00:39:07,283 --> 00:39:08,518
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come in for a minute.</font>

532
00:39:21,497 --> 00:39:22,799
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

533
00:39:29,605 --> 00:39:34,344
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't fall for you just because
we happened to be together.</font>

534
00:39:38,548 --> 00:39:41,017
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You have too much doubt about me.</font>

535
00:39:43,119 --> 00:39:44,120
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

536
00:39:46,289 --> 00:39:47,790
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But...
-No buts!</font>

537
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:53,363
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How I feel is not for you to decide.</font>

538
00:39:55,398 --> 00:39:57,100
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's true, but...</font>

539
00:40:04,841 --> 00:40:06,109
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry about today.</font>

540
00:40:09,078 --> 00:40:10,079
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's okay.</font>

541
00:40:12,281 --> 00:40:13,349
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

542
00:40:19,322 --> 00:40:20,923
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You already apologized.</font>

543
00:40:21,024 --> 00:40:22,191
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even so,</font>

544
00:40:24,861 --> 00:40:26,362
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't have much of a choice,</font>

545
00:40:27,030 --> 00:40:30,099
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but still, I brought Saeko to your place.</font>

546
00:40:33,069 --> 00:40:34,070
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

547
00:40:37,807 --> 00:40:39,175
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was awful.</font>

548
00:40:40,176 --> 00:40:41,244
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

549
00:40:47,650 --> 00:40:50,286
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You had no choice, so I forgive you.</font>

550
00:40:54,390 --> 00:40:58,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I never imagined she was
such a bad drunk though.</font>

551
00:41:22,819 --> 00:41:25,755
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everyone's next door.</font>

552
00:41:27,323 --> 00:41:31,127
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes... That's right.</font>

553
00:41:31,828 --> 00:41:33,229
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

554
00:41:48,311 --> 00:41:51,881
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">After all the trouble she caused...
She's sleeping so comfortably.</font>

555
00:41:58,087 --> 00:41:59,789
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just a bit more work left.</font>

556
00:42:01,290 --> 00:42:02,458
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let me help.</font>

557
00:42:03,359 --> 00:42:04,460
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

558
00:42:19,008 --> 00:42:20,309
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's hard, isn't it?</font>

559
00:42:23,779 --> 00:42:26,182
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hiding your feelings.</font>

560
00:42:34,090 --> 00:42:35,291
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know.</font>

561
00:42:36,926 --> 00:42:38,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It really is hard.</font>

562
00:43:08,324 --> 00:43:10,226
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry I'm so late.</font>

563
00:43:10,326 --> 00:43:13,062
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I'd better get back to work.</font>

564
00:43:14,964 --> 00:43:16,832
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is hard to do.</font>

565
00:43:20,736 --> 00:43:22,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You did it!</font>

566
00:43:26,442 --> 00:43:28,844
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">GO FOR IT!
UNBEATABLE ACE DAICHI SHINOZAKI</font>

567
00:43:28,911 --> 00:43:30,313
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can give this to him now.</font>

568
00:43:36,552 --> 00:43:37,954
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase?</font>

569
00:43:42,225 --> 00:43:43,159
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

570
00:43:50,733 --> 00:43:51,968
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

571
00:43:52,068 --> 00:43:54,971
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no! I'm late! I'm going to be late!</font>

572
00:44:03,412 --> 00:44:05,181
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sorry.</font>

573
00:44:12,822 --> 00:44:15,992
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you too, Saeko.</font>

574
00:44:20,830 --> 00:44:22,064
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hang in there.</font>

575
00:44:58,501 --> 00:44:59,435
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase.</font>

576
00:45:07,376 --> 00:45:09,211
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you here just to send us off?</font>

577
00:45:10,012 --> 00:45:10,846
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

578
00:45:11,380 --> 00:45:12,748
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wanted to give you something too.</font>

579
00:45:13,416 --> 00:45:14,250
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

580
00:45:16,385 --> 00:45:17,386
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

581
00:45:31,567 --> 00:45:32,835
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

582
00:45:37,940 --> 00:45:39,141
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See, I...</font>

583
00:45:41,077 --> 00:45:44,080
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like you, Daichi.</font>

584
00:45:49,752 --> 00:45:50,986
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I always have.</font>

585
00:45:58,694 --> 00:46:01,597
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, I...</font>

586
00:46:01,664 --> 00:46:04,100
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's okay. I understand.</font>

587
00:46:08,938 --> 00:46:11,073
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm sorry.
-Don't apologize like that.</font>

588
00:46:21,384 --> 00:46:24,653
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I have one favor to ask you.</font>

589
00:46:27,656 --> 00:46:32,862
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want us to talk and goof around
like we always have</font>

590
00:46:36,265 --> 00:46:40,569
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and stay good friends.</font>

591
00:46:41,904 --> 00:46:43,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course.</font>

592
00:46:47,610 --> 00:46:48,577
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

593
00:46:52,148 --> 00:46:54,250
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well. Good luck!</font>

594
00:46:54,850 --> 00:46:57,052
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And please give everyone these.</font>

595
00:46:59,054 --> 00:47:00,923
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't forgive you if you lose.</font>

596
00:47:15,404 --> 00:47:16,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase!</font>

597
00:47:20,743 --> 00:47:22,011
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase.</font>

598
00:47:26,982 --> 00:47:27,850
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How?</font>

599
00:47:31,020 --> 00:47:33,889
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How can you be friends
with Yoshikawa, Daichi?</font>

600
00:47:37,259 --> 00:47:39,428
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll never be strong enough
to be like that.</font>

601
00:47:47,369 --> 00:47:48,571
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I knew it.</font>

602
00:47:50,706 --> 00:47:52,975
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It doesn't seem like
I'll be able to stay friends with you.</font>

603
00:47:57,012 --> 00:47:58,180
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

604
00:48:19,735 --> 00:48:20,703
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa?</font>

605
00:48:26,275 --> 00:48:27,343
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa.</font>

606
00:48:33,015 --> 00:48:35,651
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is something wrong?</font>

607
00:50:16,118 --> 00:50:19,488
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS DRAMA IS FICTIONAL.</font>

608
00:50:19,555 --> 00:50:21,557
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Subtitle translation by
Kumar Sivasubramanian</font>
